{"tid":439754,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"識飲酒飲到唔同味？","createTime":"2017-10-18T06:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T09:56:37.000Z","uid":26215,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7a7ab2059749ecbb810b3211621fa325f78f4e","tid":439754,"uid":26215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"唔講高價酒 <br />\n普通啤酒 只講味道 有咩咁好飲<br />\n我唔識飲酒 飲親就好快頭痛 唔舒服 又凈係飲到苦<br />\n所以覺得飲酒好無謂 <br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講 人生仲苦果D <br />\n<br />\n其實個味係點 好似飲茶咁 有D人凈係飲到苦 有D人飲到甘 酒呢？"},{"pid":"f5b77b72f33efc29649fe763f5af5a06afa84c9d","tid":439754,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"其實以平價酒黎講都有千千萬萬款<br />\n覺得唔啱飲咪問下飲開既朋友有無其他推介，實有啲係啱口味既<br />\n例如普通清啤覺得太苦，咪試下甜甜地1664嗰啲"},{"pid":"829be1f86dc0faba78a015db57e3b601b99c28cc","tid":439754,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:23:33.000Z","msg":"大把酒都唔苦，不過你話咁易頭痛，就唔好飲啦"},{"pid":"bc20c63279126bbef50097fe5fea87bf29e6cb5e","tid":439754,"uid":41836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:25:38.000Z","msg":"小朋友 飲返氣水啦"},{"pid":"e122cc55d22bc1ad7fd24235e521cf4779e41a3a","tid":439754,"uid":17176,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小朋友 飲返氣水啦</blockquote><br />\n呢啲撚屌既回應真係睇見就炆<br />\n文不對題 人地問鳩你係咪會有唔同味 <br />\n你就叫人地返去飲汽水 覆個9唔搭8既comment 出黎<br />\n以為自己識飲酒係到扮大人好威？ 傻閪 笑緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ccb23e6c371ffab63da8fae9e9b6adbb3fb1f3","tid":439754,"uid":26215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小朋友 飲返氣水啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我雖然唔識飲 但都冇諗過學飲<br />\n只係好奇問下<br />\n<br />\n怪唔得愈黎愈多小學雞買酒飲 <br />\n就係你呢種飲酒=成熟 既on9思維"},{"pid":"d4286a24613be495d5a442edcf4e55321ff8c4a2","tid":439754,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:32:08.000Z","msg":"識分部份啤酒"},{"pid":"4551a12576e0f319649f7f4795fc521accaa406e","tid":439754,"uid":134834,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"當樓主30歲之時，<br />\n可能已經係飛黃騰達，又可能是件垃圾廢青，<br />\n然後不經意走返來連登，再睇返自己當年出過呢個POST，<br />\n唔知果一刻既樓主，<br />\n會笑自己戇鳩定笑自己柒撚懵懵食甜筒呢?"},{"pid":"583fa02f0a0581bcb5fab2a17aed6fd6b60cc501","tid":439754,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大把酒都唔苦，不過你話咁易頭痛，就唔好飲啦</blockquote><br />\n雞尾酒正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7486c19f0c671f919b55b027acbaa60ca2d288","tid":439754,"uid":9390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:47:55.000Z","msg":"飲雞尾酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啤酒真係唔識欣賞"},{"pid":"84cb8d00cd80781cb8f7d475abc036eda1d65602","tid":439754,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:49:16.000Z","msg":"飲威啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16cc5cfae2ef081b83a74aa52a873d5a2d25d5e","tid":439754,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"飲耐左自然唔會覺得苦<br />\n我自己就鍾意啤酒果種麥味<br />\n黑啤黎講erdinger都唔錯"},{"pid":"01a19ddaca45e2b98e8bedf8008a77ffc23e1901","tid":439754,"uid":153441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:56:37.000Z","msg":"反而我為飲酒係因為有high既感覺 久而久之就成日飲但飲得多都係頂唔順 1664最易入口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}